{"tid":1369532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小心極醜惡布袋戰術","createTime":"2019-07-26T17:16:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T17:42:52.000Z","uid":33797,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"28ce04a39c19e41ff2b7dc8e182b9d89c5a8429f","tid":1369532,"uid":33797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:16:28.000Z","msg":"警渣用布袋戰術係人都知啦，有冇諗過有醜惡版<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n班渣會布袋我地，但今次個布袋出口係向鄉村。當佢地收袋嘅時候，我地要向鄉村方向逃走，而果d位就係白衫埋伏攻擊我地嘅地方 <br />\n<br />\n即使班渣拉唔到我地，我地都會俾恐怖分子襲擊<br />\n<br />\n所以要適時散，我地之後仲有中上環<br />\n<br />\n祝大家武運亨昌"},{"pid":"fdb0e9da7c7a4298aeca380570d6a3b91d5c74d1","tid":1369532,"uid":276208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:17:17.000Z","msg":"借位一用<br />\n<br />\n<strong>請幫推到鄉民見到，希望聽日可以相安無事</strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">誠懇請鄉民今次真係要<ins>阻止任何可疑人士（包括疑似示威者）入村</ins>，唔係又引起誤會／衝突就唔好啦~~ </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n[投訴懶人包] 反對套丁及冒充原居民 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1369127\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1369127</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: blue;\">齊上齊落，支持五大訴求<br />\n支持圍村去黑，還我平靜鄉郊<br />\n反恐反黑，由投訴撚做起</span></em>"},{"pid":"ecebcc8fe8fb7b139fba38bd08a1f2a79f424ca1","tid":1369532,"uid":33797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:17:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb3924593248452b87f075e03e74a0d0211cdad1","tid":1369532,"uid":33797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:18:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee12babe339bdcb947c59e8a185526428f5d79ca","tid":1369532,"uid":33797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:19:27.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"f87e363e8bb651d299e30b8cda5d1e9b467f8431","tid":1369532,"uid":33797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:42:52.000Z","msg":"推"}]}